## Summary

I have implemented the thermal chamber hysteresis controller in `$TMPDIR/embedded_agent_eval_matrix/20260327T185742Z/thermal_chamber_hysteresis__oneshot_blind__qwen35-35b-a3b-ud-q4km/workspace/components/controller/controller.c` according to the specification in `docs/10_task.md`:

**Control Policy Implemented:**
- **On boot**: Heater off (SAFE_OFF state)
- **TEMP < 47°C**: Turn heater ON (HEATING state)
- **TEMP > 52°C**: Turn heater OFF (SAFE_OFF state)
- **47°C ≤ TEMP < 50°C**: Hold previous safe actuator state (HOLDING state)
- **50°C ≤ TEMP ≤ 52°C**: 
  - If temperature is rising compared to previous sample: turn heater OFF early (HOLDING state)
  - If not rising: hold previous safe actuator state (HOLDING state)
- **Malformed input / SENSOR_TIMEOUT**: Turn heater OFF (SAFE_OFF state)
- **Stale sensor data (>1000ms)**: Turn heater OFF (SAFE_OFF state)

